reviewText: A Brilliant & Funny Look into the Lives of Some Beautiful & Competitive Young Ladies !!! - The Interaction between them is Smooth & Deliberate; & the Whole Cast was Wisely Chosen ! - The Ladies are All Lovely; But None is More Becoming than Terissa Kelton ! With Her BatMan T-Shirt, She's Hotter than anyone else Playing BatGirl or CatWoman !!! Terissa also Delivers a Powerful Acting Performance, as does the Rest of the Cast !!! - There are Many Memorable Scenes & Lines; & I'll be Watching It Again Soon !!! - Well WORTH the Price !!!
